### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001

### ============================================================
### CLEAN PAYLOAD (success)
### ============================================================

### POST clean payload (expect 201 DiagnosticReport)
POST {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "ServiceRequest",
  "id": "ORDER-001",
  "subject": {
    "reference": "Patient/PAC-001"
  },
  "code": {
    "coding": [{
      "system": "http://loinc.org",
      "code": "HEM-001",
      "display": "Hemograma"
    }]
  }
}

